## Architecture

**The Intention Keeper takes a stand.**

Intentions rooted in harm, violence, hatred, or destruction **will not be encoded**. The system analyzes consciousness alignment, meeting harmful patterns with immediate reversal—180-degree logic that transforms negativity into its opposite.

**Hard Blocks**: Violence, hate, sexual harm, self-destruction → Forced reframe, no exceptions

**Soft Warnings**: Limiting beliefs, scarcity mindset → Suggested reframe with option to override

