## Technical Stack

**Frontend**: Pure HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)

**Cryptography**: Web Crypto API (SHA-256)

**Rendering**: HTML5 Canvas (2D Context)

**Mathematics**: Spherical coordinate systems, rose curves, radial symmetry

**Animation**: RequestAnimationFrame for 60fps rendering

**Hosting**: GitHub Pages

No frameworks. No build tools. No tracking. Just **pure, transparent code**.

